   <conbody>
      <p class="- topic/p ">Use this menu to synchronize the system with the forming machine.<ul id="ul_hqg_tk3_fcc" class="- topic/ul ">
            <li class="- topic/li ">Press Start Synchronization in order to start the process.</li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">Make sure at least 80% of the bottles are on the conveyor belt during
               synchronization.</li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">When all the bottle images are displayed in the correct sections, synchronization is
               completed. <p class="- topic/p ">In the image below, the bottle intensity is going from low to high, and
                  the synchronization is correct. </p>
               <note type="note" id="note_iqg_tk3_fcc" class="- topic/note ">
                  <p class="- topic/p "> If the synchronization is not correct, check the conveyor order in the Job
                     Settings menu.</p>
               </note>
